description: RocketCat is an oscilloscope-themed robot and a proud member of the WebtrES club. With its vibrant rossoCorsa box and classic buttons, RocketCat stands out in any crowd. Its arms and legs are designed like rockets, allowing it to navigate through the digital realm with speed and agility. The screen of RocketCat features an adorable cat, bringing a touch of charm and playfulness to its appearance. Equipped with advanced technology and a passion for exploration, RocketCat is ready to analyze and display digital waveforms with exceptional accuracy and precision.
name: RocketCat
